The manually curated USDA technical records are adapted from publications of
the USDA Forest Service, Forest Products Laboratory. The North American
hardwood profiles use FPL–GTR–83; the Northern red oak profile also uses
FPL–RP–378; the North American softwood profiles use FPL–GTR–102; and the
tropical profiles use Agriculture Handbook 607:

https://www.fpl.fs.usda.gov/documnts/fplgtr/fplgtr83.pdf
https://www.fpl.fs.usda.gov/documnts/fplrp/fplrp378.pdf
https://www.fpl.fs.usda.gov/documnts/fplgtr/fplgtr102.pdf
https://research.fs.usda.gov/download/treesearch/69634.pdf

No endorsement by the USDA Forest Service or Forest Products Laboratory is
implied.

Brazilian wood-property records are adapted from the Brazilian Woods Database
published by the Brazilian Forest Service (Serviço Florestal Brasileiro) and
its Forest Products Laboratory (Laboratório de Produtos Florestais, LPF/SFB):

https://dados.florestal.gov.br/dataset/banco-de-dados-de-madeiras-brasileiras-do-lpf-sfb
https://lpf.florestal.gov.br/en-us/brazilian-woods

The dataset metadata identifies the material as Creative Commons Attribution
4.0 (CC BY 4.0):

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The imported values consolidate laboratory observations collected between
1981 and 1997. No endorsement by the Brazilian Forest Service or LPF/SFB is
implied.

Supplemental Brazilian fungal- and termite-resistance classifications are
adapted as short factual records from the São Paulo Institute for
Technological Research (Instituto de Pesquisas Tecnológicas, IPT) wood
information service:

https://madeiras.ipt.br/

Each adapted record links to its individual IPT source page. Descriptive
prose, photographs, and illustrations from the IPT pages are not redistributed.
No endorsement by IPT is implied.

Supplemental botanical classification, distribution, physical-property, and
durability values are adapted as short factual records from Lignumdata:

https://lignumdata.ch/system/holzarten?locale=en

Each adapted record links to its individual Lignumdata source page. Descriptive
prose, photographs, illustrations, and other media from Lignumdata are not
redistributed. No endorsement by Lignum or Lignumdata is implied.

